I simply needed a small space to store some excess bits and pieces between seasons. The space I eventually rented is about the size of a long, shallow closet. For $17 a month, which is less then I expected, I can eliminate having my apartment cluttered with things I won't need until summer. To quote Martha Stewart, it's a good thing!
